lead_paragraph: Raul Rodriguez's header went off the cross bar and goalkeeper Alec Kann's back in the fourth minute of stoppage time to give the Houston Dynamo a 3-3 draw with Sporting Kansas City on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Stoppage Goal Gives Dynamo 3-3 Draw With Sporting KC
